metrics_conclusion: The Singularity Song has higher complexity than the average song  in terms Chord-Bass Melody.
key_conclusion:
The Singularity Song is written in the key of C Major.  

According to the Theorytab database, it is the most common key in all of popular music. 

See the C Major Cheat Sheet for popular chords, chord progressions, downloadable midi files and more!

metadata.editComments: It was hard for me to pick out the guitar chords. I hope I didn't overchart it, but at the same time, I like the complex chords and should try to remember them next time I make a song.
